<h2><span>著作信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>SCP-CN-1559</strong> - 青鸟<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/re-spectators" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3722555); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3722555&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607780966" alt="Re_spectators" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3722555)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/re-spectators" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3722555); return false;">Re_spectators</a></span></p>
<p>本文的创作过程得到了许多站内朋友的大力相助。这里希望特别感谢一下帮助我完善故事情节发展的<span class="error-inline"><em>readeiier</em> does not match any existing user name</span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3967806&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607780966" alt="ShineShadowD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3967806)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;">ShineShadowD</a></span>和帮助我补充设定、完善文言文部分的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simon-arran" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4354147); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4354147&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607780966" alt="Simon Arran" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4354147)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simon-arran" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4354147); return false;">Simon Arran</a></span>等几位朋友表示衷心的感谢！</p>
<p>此外，还有许多朋友为这篇文章提出了宝贵且有价值的建议。在这里感谢所有帮助这篇作品变得更好的各位对我的帮助！</p>
<p>作者本人能力有限，作品可能还有许多不足之处，恳请各位批评指正。谢谢大家！</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>图像信息：</strong></p>
<p>（第一迭代）<br />
青鸟的图片来自下列两张CC0（公有领域）图片的二次创作：<br />
<a href="https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/cn/view-image.php?image=223503&amp;picture=">https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/cn/view-image.php?image=223503&amp;picture=</a><br />
<a href="https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:%EC%A1%B0%EC%84%A0-%EC%B2%AD_%EC%99%B8%EA%B5%90%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C(%EC%9E%90%EB%AC%B8)_280.jpg">https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:%EC%A1%B0%EC%84%A0-%EC%B2%AD_%EC%99%B8%EA%B5%90%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C(%EC%9E%90%EB%AC%B8)_280.jpg</a><br />
（请注意：第二张图片仅在著作权法规定著作权保留至作者死后70年或更短的国家/地区才属于公有领域。在中国大陆，这一规定为50年。）</p>
<p>分级“Necropsar”的图标由光影<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3967806&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607780966" alt="ShineShadowD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3967806)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;">ShineShadowD</a></span><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/more-acs-icons">制作</a>。</p>
<p>（第四迭代）<br />
AG-99的图片来自对下列CC0（公有领域）图片的二次创作：<br />
<a href="https://publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=180332&amp;picture=space-shuttle-endeavour-landing">https://publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=180332&amp;picture=space-shuttle-endeavour-landing</a></p>
<p>经作者本人更动或创作的图片依循CC BY-SA 3.0协议发布。</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+622</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
